title: Hellstrøm Inviterer
overview: Eyvind Hellstrøm invites several of Norway's biggest celebrities for a friendly chef's duel in the kitchen. In each episode of Hellstrøm Inviterer, the chef gets a visit from a celebrity to make one of their favorite dishes. Hellstrøm will be making the same dish, and in this unpretentious duel it will be determined a winner between the two.
